divs: sighting detailsat approximately 9:40 while sitting outside a white light followed by approx. 7 red lights initially in a straight line moved from the southwest towards northeast in a long gradual curve gradually forming into a v-form much like a geese pattern towards the north over clinch mountain. then approx. one minute later had completed a turn and was then formed into a diamond shape and were heading back towards the east. we lost sight of the lights due to the tree line. the distance estimate would be 8-10 miles overhead and mph would be around 1000-1500. because of the lack of sound and mobility of the objects\object it did not fit any type of military or civilian aircraft profile.
Summary: Bright white light followed by several red lights soundless and changing position.
